      <p class="ess-section__intro">Local development servers replicate production environments on your machine, enabling offline development and testing without deploying to remote servers. Essential for web development, they provide Apache/Nginx web servers, MySQL/PostgreSQL databases, and PHP/Python runtimes in pre-configured packages.</p>

