        <div class="ess-tool__body">
          <p>Laragon represents modern thinking about local development servers. It's fast — starting servers takes seconds. Auto virtual host creation makes each project accessible via pretty URLs automatically. Support extends beyond PHP to Node.js, Python, Ruby, and Go.</p>

          <div class="ess-tool__pros-cons">
            <div class="ess-tool__pros">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--pros">Pros</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Incredibly fast and lightweight</li>
                <li>Auto virtual hosts save configuration time</li>
                <li>Supports multiple languages and frameworks</li>
                <li>Truly portable with no system modifications</li>
                <li>Completely free</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="ess-tool__cons">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--cons">Cons</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Windows only</li>
                <li>Less documentation than XAMPP</li>
                <li>Smaller community</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== SECTION 12: DOCUMENTATION GENERATORS ========== -->
  <section id="documentation-generators" class="ess-section" aria-label="Documentation generators">
