      <p class="ess-section__intro">Documentation generators create professional documentation websites from code comments and markdown files. Essential for maintaining technical documentation that stays synchronized with code.</p>

      <!-- ===== Sphinx ===== -->
      <article class="ess-tool" id="sphinx">
        <div class="ess-tool__header">
          <div class="ess-tool__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line></svg>
