          <span class="tag">Windows</span>
          <span class="tag">macOS</span>
          <span class="tag">Linux</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ess-tool__body">
          <p>JSDoc generates API documentation from specially-formatted comments in JavaScript code. TypeScript support and IDE autocompletion from JSDoc comments makes it valuable even without generating docs.</p>

          <div class="ess-tool__pros-cons">
            <div class="ess-tool__pros">
