          <p>OpenAPI (formerly Swagger) is the industry standard for REST API documentation. Swagger UI generates interactive documentation where users can explore and test API endpoints directly in the browser. Most API frameworks include OpenAPI support — auto-generating specs from code.</p>

          <div class="ess-tool__pros-cons">
            <div class="ess-tool__pros">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--pros">Pros</h4>
