        <div class="ess-tool__body">
          <p>MkDocs generates documentation sites from Markdown files with minimal configuration. The Material for MkDocs theme produces beautiful, responsive documentation. Live reloading during development shows changes instantly. Many open-source projects have migrated to MkDocs for its simplicity.</p>

