      </div>
      <p class="ess-section__intro">Modern applications require visibility into performance, errors, and user experience. Monitoring and observability tools collect metrics, logs, and traces to help diagnose issues, optimize performance, and understand system behavior.</p>

      <!-- ===== New Relic ===== -->
      <article class="ess-tool" id="new-relic">
        <div class="ess-tool__header">
          <div class="ess-tool__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"></path></svg>
