        </div>
        <div class="ess-tool__tags">
          <span class="tag tag-free">Free Tier</span>
          <span class="tag tag-paid">From $99/mo</span>
          <span class="tag">Cloud SaaS</span>
          <span class="tag">All Platforms</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ess-tool__body">
          <p>New Relic provides comprehensive observability across your entire stack — applications, infrastructure, logs, and user experience. APM automatically instruments applications to track transaction times, database queries, and errors. The free tier provides 100GB monthly data ingestion.</p>

          <div class="ess-tool__pros-cons">
            <div class="ess-tool__pros">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--pros">Pros</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Comprehensive all-in-one platform</li>
                <li>Easy setup with automatic instrumentation</li>
                <li>Excellent distributed tracing</li>
                <li>Generous free tier</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="ess-tool__cons">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--cons">Cons</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Can get expensive at scale</li>
                <li>Data retention limits</li>
                <li>Query language learning curve</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- ===== Datadog ===== -->
      <article class="ess-tool" id="datadog">
        <div class="ess-tool__header">
          <div class="ess-tool__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline></svg>
