          <p>Datadog excels at monitoring cloud infrastructure with over 600 integrations. Service maps automatically visualize dependencies between microservices, databases, and APIs. Machine learning-based anomaly detection catches issues before they impact users.</p>

          <div class="ess-tool__pros-cons">
            <div class="ess-tool__pros">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--pros">Pros</h4>
