          <p>The most popular open-source monitoring stack, especially in Kubernetes environments. Prometheus scrapes metrics via HTTP endpoints. Grafana creates rich dashboards. Together they provide enterprise-grade monitoring without licensing costs.</p>

          <div class="ess-tool__pros-cons">
            <div class="ess-tool__pros">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--pros">Pros</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Completely free and open source</li>
