          <p>Sentry specializes in error tracking with exceptional developer experience. Full context with stack traces, breadcrumbs, release versions, and source maps. Issue grouping uses ML to cluster similar errors. Integration with GitHub, Jira, and Slack. Free tier includes 5,000 monthly events.</p>

          <div class="ess-tool__pros-cons">
            <div class="ess-tool__pros">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--pros">Pros</h4>
