        <div class="ess-tool__header">
          <div class="ess-tool__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83 2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1 0-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83-2.83l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 4 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 2.83l-.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 19.4 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 0 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ess-tool__title-wrap">
            <h3 class="ess-tool__name">Jenkins</h3>
            <p class="ess-tool__tagline">Self-hosted automation server</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ess-tool__tags">
          <span class="tag tag-free">Free</span>
          <span class="tag tag-oss">Open Source</span>
          <span class="tag">Self-hosted</span>
          <span class="tag">All Platforms</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ess-tool__body">
          <p>Jenkins remains the most widely used CI/CD tool with over 1,800 plugins. Pipelines defined in Groovy-based Jenkinsfiles provide version-controlled build configurations. Self-hosting provides complete control over infrastructure and security.</p>

          <div class="ess-tool__pros-cons">
            <div class="ess-tool__pros">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--pros">Pros</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Completely free with unlimited usage</li>
                <li>Unmatched flexibility (1,800+ plugins)</li>
                <li>Self-hosted for complete control</li>
                <li>Mature and battle-tested</li>
                <li>Works with any technology stack</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="ess-tool__cons">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--cons">Cons</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Steep learning curve</li>
                <li>Requires infrastructure management</li>
                <li>UI feels dated</li>
                <li>Plugin quality varies</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- ===== GitHub Actions ===== -->
      <article class="ess-tool" id="github-actions">
        <div class="ess-tool__header">
          <div class="ess-tool__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ess-tool__title-wrap">
            <h3 class="ess-tool__name">GitHub Actions</h3>
            <p class="ess-tool__tagline">Native GitHub CI/CD automation</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ess-tool__tags">
          <span class="tag tag-free">Free Public Repos</span>
          <span class="tag tag-paid">$0.008/minute</span>
          <span class="tag">Cloud SaaS</span>
          <span class="tag">GitHub Integration</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ess-tool__body">
          <p>GitHub Actions integrates CI/CD directly into GitHub repositories. YAML workflows trigger on push, pull requests, schedules, or manual events. The Actions marketplace provides thousands of pre-built actions. Free unlimited minutes for public repositories.</p>

          <div class="ess-tool__pros-cons">
            <div class="ess-tool__pros">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--pros">Pros</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Seamless GitHub integration</li>
                <li>Free for public repositories</li>
                <li>Large marketplace of actions</li>
                <li>Simple YAML syntax</li>
                <li>Matrix builds for parallel testing</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="ess-tool__cons">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--cons">Cons</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Limited to GitHub</li>
                <li>Minutes cost adds up</li>
                <li>Less flexible than Jenkins</li>
                <li>Debugging workflows can be frustrating</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- ===== GitLab CI/CD ===== -->
      <article class="ess-tool" id="gitlab-ci">
        <div class="ess-tool__header">
          <div class="ess-tool__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22.65 14.39L12 22.13 1.35 14.39a.84.84 0 0 1-.3-.94l1.22-3.78 2.44-7.51A.42.42 0 0 1 4.82 2a.43.43 0 0 1 .58 0 .42.42 0 0 1 .11.18l2.44 7.49h8.1l2.44-7.51A.42.42 0 0 1 18.6 2a.43.43 0 0 1 .58 0 .42.42 0 0 1 .11.18l2.44 7.51L23 13.45a.84.84 0 0 1-.35.94z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ess-tool__title-wrap">
            <h3 class="ess-tool__name">GitLab CI/CD</h3>
            <p class="ess-tool__tagline">Built-in GitLab DevOps platform</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ess-tool__tags">
          <span class="tag tag-free">Free Tier</span>
          <span class="tag tag-paid">From $29/user/mo</span>
          <span class="tag">Cloud SaaS</span>
          <span class="tag">Self-hosted</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ess-tool__body">
          <p>GitLab provides a complete DevOps platform with integrated CI/CD. Auto DevOps provides pre-configured pipelines. Built-in container registry, review apps, and Kubernetes integration. Free tier includes 400 CI/CD minutes monthly.</p>

          <div class="ess-tool__pros-cons">
            <div class="ess-tool__pros">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--pros">Pros</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Complete DevOps platform in one tool</li>
                <li>Auto DevOps reduces configuration</li>
                <li>Built-in container registry</li>
                <li>Review apps simplify testing</li>
                <li>Self-hosted option</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="ess-tool__cons">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--cons">Cons</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Limited free tier minutes (400/month)</li>
                <li>Requires GitLab for Git hosting</li>
                <li>Self-hosted version resource-intensive</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- ===== CircleCI ===== -->
      <article class="ess-tool" id="circleci">
        <div class="ess-tool__header">
          <div class="ess-tool__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ess-tool__title-wrap">
            <h3 class="ess-tool__name">CircleCI</h3>
            <p class="ess-tool__tagline">Cloud-native CI/CD with Docker-first approach</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ess-tool__tags">
          <span class="tag tag-free">Free Tier</span>
          <span class="tag tag-paid">From $30/mo</span>
          <span class="tag">Cloud SaaS</span>
          <span class="tag">Self-hosted Option</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ess-tool__body">
          <p>CircleCI pioneered the Docker-based CI/CD approach. Each build runs in a clean container for reproducible builds. Orbs provide reusable configuration packages. Free tier includes 6,000 build minutes monthly.</p>

          <div class="ess-tool__pros-cons">
            <div class="ess-tool__pros">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--pros">Pros</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Fast builds with excellent caching</li>
                <li>Docker-first approach</li>
                <li>Orbs simplify configurations</li>
                <li>Good free tier (6,000 minutes)</li>
                <li>SSH debugging</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="ess-tool__cons">
              <h4 class="ess-tool__subtitle ess-tool__subtitle--cons">Cons</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>YAML configuration can be complex</li>
                <li>Steeper learning curve</li>
                <li>Minutes cost adds up</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
